    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 47,764₽ | 物品价值: 14,288 | Mechanic报价: 8,001₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 28,368₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级1 < 228$ ≈ 27,400₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Western Connection - Part 2 @ Skier\n\nMP9（MP 即德语“冲锋枪”之意），是瑞士 Brügger&Thomet 公司设计制造的一款可选开火模式的冲锋枪，发射 9x19 好木帕拉贝鲁姆手枪弹。是个人防卫武器 (PDW) 的绝佳之选。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 47,764₽ | 物品价值: 14,288 | Mechanic报价: 8,001₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 28,368₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级1 < 228$ ≈ 27,400₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Western Connection - Part 2 @ Skier\n\nThe Brügger & Thomet MP9 (Maschinenpistole 9mm, German for machine pistol) is a selective-fire 9x19mm Parabellum caliber machine pistol designed and manufactured by Brügger & Thomet of Switzerland. A perfect choice for a Personal Defense Weapon (PDW)."
    },
